### Get cart for user
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cart/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Add item to cart
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cart/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

### Update cart item quantity
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/cart/1/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "quantity": 5
}

### Remove item from cart
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/cart/1/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Clear cart
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/cart/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN